Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.basic

Class OrdinalSyntaxTree<Cargo>

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.basic.OrdinalSyntaxTree<Cargo>
Type Parameters:
Cargo - any king of data associated with the tree elements
All Implemented Interfaces:
SyntaxTreeInterface<Cargo>
public class OrdinalSyntaxTree<Cargo>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SyntaxTreeInterface<Cargo>

This class is an ordinal implementation of SyntaxTreeInterface interface. It can be used everywhere when AndOrTree can.

This class is not thread-safe

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
SyntaxTreeInterface, JUnit tests
